BMaggregator
============

BMaggregator tracks chans and subscriptions (broadcasts and mailing lists).
It publishes daily activity reports.

To use:
-Setup a new bitmessage client, with api enabled.
-Create a file named "config" with the api information. (See exampleconfig)
-Create a similar file named "handlerconfig". (See examplehandlerconfig)
-Put handlerconfig in the directory that the bitmessage client is running from.
-In keys.dat set the apinotifypath to handler.py. Example:
  "apinotifypath=/home/user/BMaggregator/handler.py"
-Start bitmessage.
-Run loop.py